items.title: Syrian refugees wait at Turkish border, eager to return home after fall of Assad's government
items.author: Associated Press
items.content:
Hundreds of Syrian refugees gathered at a border crossing in southern Turkey on Monday, eagerly anticipating their return home following the fall of President Bashar Assad’s government. Many arrived at the two crossings, Cilvegozu and Oncupinar, at daybreak, draped in blankets and coats. Read more: https://bit.ly/3OPE1KU
(AP Video shot by Mehmet Guzel/Mucahit Ceylan)

items.author: Associated Press
items.content:

items.title: Israel's Netanyahu testifies in court in a corruption trial
items.author: Associated Press
items.content:
Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu was set to take the stand on Tuesday in his long-running trial for alleged corruption. It is the first time an Israeli prime minister will take the stand as a criminal defendant, an embarrassing milestone for a leader who has tried to cultivate an image as a sophisticated and respected statesman. items.title: 2024 Nobel Prize LIVE: Science and Literature laureates honored by Sweden’s King Carl XVI Gustaf
items.author: Associated Press
items.content:
The Nobel Prize laureates in Science and Literature receive a diploma and medal from King Carl XVI Gustaf of Sweden.
Here’s a list of the 2024 Nobel Prize winners:

The Nobel Prize in Physics
John J. Hopfield, Geoffrey Hinton

The Nobel Prize in Chemistry
David Baker, Demis Hassabis, John Jumper

The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine
Victor Ambros, Gary Ruvkun

The Nobel Prize in Literature
Han Kang

#nobelprize #sweden #stockholm #news #live

items.title: Jay-Z says lawsuit accusing him of rape part of extortion ploy I AP Explains
items.author: Associated Press
items.content:
Jay-Z says a rape allegation made against him is part of an extortion attempt.
A woman who previously sued Sean “Diddy” Combs, alleging she was raped at an awards show after-party in 2000 when she was 13, amended the lawsuit Sunday to include a new allegation that Jay-Z was also at the party and participated in the sexual assault.
